    <p class="qowt-li-0_0 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 5pt 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-1-0 1; counter-reset: lc-1-1 0 lc-1-2 0 lc-1-3 0 lc-1-4 0 lc-1-5 0 lc-1-6 0 lc-1-7 0 lc-1-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;">Est-elle en mesure d&rsquo;accro&icirc;tre sa production, de tenir la route en terme de qualit&eacute; et de comp&eacute;titivit&eacute; ?</span></p>
    <p class="qowt-li-0_0 qowt-list" is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 5pt 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36pt; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px; position: relative; counter-increment: lc-1-0 1; counter-reset: lc-1-1 0 lc-1-2 0 lc-1-3 0 lc-1-4 0 lc-1-5 0 lc-1-6 0 lc-1-7 0 lc-1-8 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12pt;">Disposez-vous des ressources humaines capables de relever le d&eacute;fi de l&rsquo;exportation, de g&eacute;rer la complexit&eacute; administrative induite ?</span></p>
