hyperlink" target="_blank"><span class="qowt-font8-SegoeUI" is="qowt-word-run" style='display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif !important; font-size: 12pt;'>succursale</span></a><span class="qowt-font8-SegoeUI" is="qowt-word-run" style='display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif !important; font-size: 12pt;'>&nbsp;ou m&ecirc;me d&rsquo;une&nbsp;</span><a contenteditable="false" href="https://bpifrance-creation.fr/encyclopedie/developper-lactivite-son-entreprise/developpement-a-linternational/filiale" is="qowt-hyperlink" target="_blank"><span class="qowt-font8-SegoeUI" is="qowt-word-run" style='display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif !important; font-size: 12pt;'>filiale</span></a><span class="qowt-font8-SegoeUI" is="qowt-word-run" style='display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif !important; font-size: 12pt;'>.</span><span class="qowt-font8-SegoeUI" is="qowt-line-break" style='font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif !important; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 49, 50);'><br></span><span class="qowt-font8-SegoeUI" is="qowt-line-break" style='font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif !important; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(51, 49, 50);'><br></span><span class="qowt-font8-SegoeUI" is="qowt-word-run" style='display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif !important; font-size: 12pt;'>Dans certains pays, il ne pourra s&rsquo;agir que d&rsquo;une&nbsp;</span><a contenteditable="false" href="https://bpifrance-creation.fr/encyclopedie/developper-lactivite-son-entreprise/developpement-a-linternational/joint-venture" is="qowt-hyperlink" target="_blank"><span class="qowt-font8-SegoeUI" is="qowt-word-run" style='display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif !important; font-size: 12pt;'>joint-venture</span></a><span class="qowt-font8-SegoeUI" is="qowt-word-run" style='display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif !important; font-size: 12pt;'>&nbsp;mont&eacute;e avec un partenaire local. Passer par un distributeur implant&eacute; localement n&rsquo;est pas toujours plus simple. Les entreprises de haute technologie doivent d&eacute;nicher les perles rares, disposant des comp&eacute;tences techniques et de la capacit&eacute; &agrave; assurer la maintenance de leurs produits de mani&egrave;re fiable.</span></p>
